#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn35.163"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn35.163:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 35 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 35 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.163:0.2"
msgid "16. Nandikkhayavagga "
msgstr "16. The End of Relishing "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 163. Koṭṭhikadukkhasutta → koṭṭhitadukkhasuttaṃ (bj) | koṭṭhiko 2 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn35.163:0.3"
msgid "163. Koṭṭhikadukkhasutta "
msgstr "163. With Koṭṭhita on Suffering "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.146, sc1
msgctxt "sn35.163:1.1"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā mahākoṭṭhiko … pe … bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then Venerable Mahākoṭṭhita … said to the Buddha: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.163:1.2"
msgid "“sādhu me, bhante … pe … vihareyyan”ti. "
msgstr "“Sir, may the Buddha please teach me Dhamma in brief. When I’ve heard it, I’ll live alone, withdrawn, diligent, keen, and resolute.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.163:1.3"
msgid "“Yaṃ kho, koṭṭhika, dukkhaṃ tatra te chando pahātabbo. "
msgstr "“Koṭṭhita, you should give up desire for what is suffering. "

msgctxt "sn35.163:1.4"
msgid "Kiñca, koṭṭhika, dukkhaṃ? "
msgstr "And what is suffering? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.163:1.5"
msgid "Cakkhu kho, koṭṭhika, dukkhaṃ; tatra te chando pahātabbo. "
msgstr "The eye, "

msgctxt "sn35.163:1.6"
msgid "Rūpā dukkhā; tatra te chando pahātabbo. "
msgstr "sights, "

msgctxt "sn35.163:1.7"
msgid "Cakkhuviññāṇaṃ dukkhaṃ; tatra te chando pahātabbo. "
msgstr "eye consciousness, "

msgctxt "sn35.163:1.8"
msgid "Cakkhusamphasso dukkho; tatra te chando pahātabbo. "
msgstr "and eye contact are suffering: you should give up desire for them. "

msgctxt "sn35.163:1.9"
msgid "Yampidaṃ cakkhusamphassapaccayā uppajjati vedayitaṃ sukhaṃ vā dukkhaṃ vā adukkhamasukhaṃ vā tampi dukkhaṃ; tatra te chando pahātabbo … pe … "
msgstr "The pleasant, painful, or neutral feeling that arises conditioned by eye contact is also suffering; you should give up desire for it. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.163:1.10"
msgid "jivhā dukkhā; tatra te chando pahātabbo … pe … "
msgstr "The ear … nose … tongue … body … "

msgctxt "sn35.163:1.11"
msgid "mano dukkho; tatra te chando pahātabbo. "
msgstr "The mind, "

msgctxt "sn35.163:1.12"
msgid "Dhammā dukkhā; tatra te chando pahātabbo. "
msgstr "thoughts, "

msgctxt "sn35.163:1.13"
msgid "Manoviññāṇaṃ dukkhaṃ; tatra te chando pahātabbo. "
msgstr "mind consciousness, "

msgctxt "sn35.163:1.14"
msgid "Manosamphasso dukkho; tatra te chando pahātabbo. "
msgstr "and mind contact are suffering: you should give up desire for them. "

msgctxt "sn35.163:1.15"
msgid "Yampidaṃ manosamphassapaccayā uppajjati vedayitaṃ sukhaṃ vā dukkhaṃ vā adukkhamasukhaṃ vā tampi dukkhaṃ; tatra te chando pahātabbo. "
msgstr "The pleasant, painful, or neutral feeling that arises conditioned by mind contact is also suffering: you should give up desire for it. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.163:1.16"
msgid "Yaṃ kho, koṭṭhika, dukkhaṃ tatra te chando pahātabbo”ti. "
msgstr "Koṭṭhita, you should give up desire for what is suffering.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn35.163:1.17"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

